{"type": "article", "id": 26363, "title": "雅诗兰黛预大规模裁员，以及，Gucci 推出四款双肩包｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-04T10:12:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 811, "name": "家居"}, {"id": 15805, "name": "双肩包"}, {"id": 14934, "name": "刺绣"}, {"id": 604, "name": "配饰"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2835, "name": "匡威"}, {"id": 27142, "name": "BUNNEY"}, {"id": 6651, "name": "Yves Saint Laurent"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 1192, "name": "Alexander McQueen"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120209l8inuzHDx7a0TcjJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Alexander-McQueen-names-Emmanuel-Gintzburger-as-CEO,689191.html#.VylAAYQrJQY\"><b>Alexander McQueen 任命新 CEO</b></a>｜Alexander McQueen 母公司开云（Kering）近日宣布，由 Emmanuel Gintzburger 担任 Alexander McQueen 公司首席执政官，5 月 9 日生效，接任已在公司 12 年的 Jonathan Akeroyd。2009 年 Gintzburger 加入 Yves Saint Laurent  任欧洲区零售总监，最近升至世界零售及批发总监。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Smashbox-M-A-C-gloss-up-Estee-Lauder-profit,688985.html#.VylFpYQrJQY\"><b>雅诗兰黛三季度销售额上涨，净收益下跌</b></a>｜美国美妆巨头雅诗兰黛（Estee Lauder ）宣布胜预期的季度利润，M.A.C. 和 Smashbox 彩妆品牌在国际市场的强劲需求拉动，由彩妆新产品的需求带动，以及在英国、意大利和中东市场扩张零售渠道，彩妆部门的销售额在截至 3 月 31 日的三季度上涨了 7% 至 11.6 亿美元。净销售额上涨了 3% 至 26.6 亿美元，净收益从 2.721 亿美元跌至 2.656 亿，有 2.4% 的幅度。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Estee-Lauder-to-cut-up-to-1-200-jobs,689024.html#.VylCsIQrJQY\"><b>雅诗兰黛预计裁员 1200 人</b></a>｜接上条，雅诗兰黛近日同时宣布重组计划，预计将裁员 900-1200 人，占到员工总数的 2.5%，预计每年能节省 2-3 亿美元。同时计划重新教育及调动部分员工，作为投资新产品、社交媒体及线上销售额的一部分。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/AmorePacific-posts-24-4-rise-in-Q1-net-profit,688703.html#rc\"><b>爱茉莉太平洋一季度利润增长 24.4%</b></a>｜韩国最著名的美妆集团爱茉莉太平洋（AmorePacific）宣布一季度净利润上涨 24.4%，达到 2630 亿韩元（约合 14.73 亿人民币），营业利润上涨了 21.5% 至 3378 亿韩元，销售额则有 23.3% 的增长，达到 14850 亿韩元。在美国地区也因为地区和渠道方面的扩张而持续增长，一季度上涨 24.1%，而欧洲区销售额则下跌了 6.4%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/gucci-unveils-pre-fall-windows-10422093/\"><b>Gucci 公布其 2016 早秋橱窗</b></a>｜Gucci 品牌创意总监 Alessandro Michele 为米兰和巴黎旗舰店设计橱窗，将在本月应用到全球旗舰店。女装橱窗以粉红色的基调，和“粉色苍鹭”的印花装饰，男装则与植物有关，中性的商品会以黄色天鹅绒为背景来展示。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120152LIoCH6yzdmYZEKi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Gucci 推出个<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/02/gucci-tech-backpack-embroidery/\">双肩包系列“techpacks”</a>，其中刺绣款非常亮眼，上面的文字 “l’aveugle par amour” 是“为爱盲目”的意思：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031201538HiRkv6hLmornWp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120153Gftku56U1QncOrW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120153JStWpgqsO2BGTFE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120154eVtKma1J5EIyL2Tu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120154QXqFjvIaKtlJT6dP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">介绍一双非常“软妹”的鞋，来自 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/04/30/bunney-converse-jack-purcell-closer-look/\">BUNNEY 和匡威新推出的联名款</a>，BUNNEY 是伦敦一个珠宝类的生活方式品牌，此次设计使用英国 Linton Tweeds 面料，后者从 1920 年起就为巴黎高定时装提供原料。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120155q389Gd4Y7QrZNKJt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120155qVvn16hyrTlMm5KO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120156fHyWFQkoqgXsehSZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120156QFxl5V01Of6WCK7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120156FacIYWQCVo42ylje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120157peGLUsYRZug3vkD5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Yves-Saint-Laurent-launches-a-road-trip-inspired-summer-makeup-collection,688634.html#.VylJ24QrJQY\">Yves Saint Laurent  推出新的夏季彩妆系列</a>，灵感来自荒漠中的公路旅行，多是自然的色调和金属色的眼妆，5 月 30 日上市：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120157pvjLrh5KMQ3d0Xge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4159292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120158wQzF3ue9ZqdVP5c8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42433234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031201580xG75NaBPKhogJt1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120159Szc4yIBwTX36AqjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70676692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">超模 Julia Nobis 为 Tiffany &amp; Co 的杂志<i> </i><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/julia-nobis-tiffany-co-magazine-jewelry/\"><i>This is Tiffany </i>最新一辑（ 2016 春夏）拍摄了黑白大片</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120159HbAsRpeWzFtMLa3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120200qfSRCpd9IiWJkb8D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120200aEXMwfLkm1dYUPnN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120201dVfgUXWOQ3Y9u18y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120201fDMUSEF40BGwZC6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/02/hm-home-summer-2016/#slide-3\">H&amp;M 家居的夏日系列出炉</a>，地中海风情和热带元素为主：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120202kQ3YCr6El4DKgN2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120202goXlHr3xQBnwJtIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120203Ug7FSTAtcjbBQi6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312020353IL29xuCaqFk7hS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120204PztZhHRrpvBfjYGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120204ICPDy1z5AbwO2ftp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120205wiMzaQKluNrvPZgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">维密天使 Stella Maxwell 近日<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/stella-maxwell-beach-fashion-elle-france/\">为法国版  ELLE 拍摄封面及大片</a>，在海滩上演绎热裤、背心、比基尼和一些波西米亚风的夏日服饰：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120206nWQ4Da3irGTksd6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031202060iLXEk1NKrwAHYgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120207NXuMLPpfE8ojgvJa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120207XPOKxpBVkIbs0aDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120208agUxck2eFC6WovDS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120208HaG5eDIquYpJnOQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}